{"tid":296792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國U20踢德國丁組　當地每隊可獲13萬元仍擬罷踢　籲「勿將聯賽變馬戲團」","createTime":"2017-06-25T02:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T03:41:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa067c8e3043da5cc964455ae849ff29c32e59c","tid":296792,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T02:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170624/s00006/8504806eb77d9b8b435b147e0c7e7a16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170624%2Fs00006%2F8504806eb77d9b8b435b147e0c7e7a16.jpg&h=6397bcc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為備戰2020年東京奧運，中國足協已和德國足協達成共識，國足U20代表隊下季將參戰德國第4級別的西南地區聯賽。雖然每隊對手將獲1.5萬歐元（13萬港元），但有該聯賽的參賽球隊就大表反對，直指把聯賽變成「馬戲團」。<br />\n<br />\n按中、德兩國足協的協議，下季德國西南地區聯賽將有19支當地球隊及國足U20，雖然後者成績將不計算聯賽積分，而且中國足協會向其他球隊各支付1.5萬歐元，但仍有球隊大力抨擊此計劃。奧伯豪森（Oberhausen）主席Hajo Sommers表示：「這把聯賽變成馬戲團，這樣拜仁慕尼黑就可向中國賣更多球衣吧。」<br />\n<br />\n紅白埃森（Rot-Wiess Essen）主席Michael Welling亦稱：「在這個聯賽，絕對有比協助中國青年球員更重要的事。」至於曼海娒（SV Waldhof Mannheim）則在facebook發表聲明，指球會已有共識拒絕與國足U20對賽，寧可另外進行兩場友賽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170624/s00006/1498307777209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170624%2Fs00006%2F1498307777209&d=fZFS8tXsTIlra8mgLvL2fNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b3854078\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170624%2Fs00006%2F1498307777209&h=41cec162\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170624/s00006/1498307777209</a>"},{"pid":"b93ebdfc3787b5cf4584a3e8ae1912c3732264ab","tid":296792,"uid":4180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T02:53:50.000Z","msg":"支那真係以為自己大撚哂??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54741eb8ad84db4846c012f347c862c142629ba","tid":296792,"uid":11753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T02:56:51.000Z","msg":"支那生番企開啲喇屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f850d784d8af9e74eb77962c4408287882e1db","tid":296792,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:00:20.000Z","msg":"好撚柒上面張相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f14cc31248ac1cd01c70b96146486e61c08ad8","tid":296792,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:03:16.000Z","msg":"支那人真係好樣衰"},{"pid":"166dd3f8eeb8e275c85db7ef0f0d013b10e5b242","tid":296792,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:41:00.000Z","msg":"拜仁中槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw，支那狗食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}